/master /Times-Roman findfont def           % Set up a standard 1 unit font to
					    % be used later in
					    % makefont-setfont operations.
master [12 0 0 12 0 0] makefont setfont     % Create a uniformly scaled 12
					    % point font.
234 504 moveto
(Type is one of the most eloquent) show
				       
master [9 0 0 12 0 0] makefont setfont      % Create a condensed 12 point
					    % font.
234 488 moveto
(means of expression in every epoch) show
					 
master [7 0 0 12 0 0] makefont setfont      % Create a very condensed 12 point
					    % font.
234 472 moveto
(of style. Next to architecture, it) show
					 
master [15 0 0 12 0 0] makefont setfont     % Create an extended 12 point
					    % font.
234 456 moveto
(gives the most characteristic) show
				    
master [17 0 0 12 0 0] makefont setfont     % Create a very extended 12 point
					    % font.
234 440 moveto
(portrait of a period and the most) show
					
master [12 0 4.36764 12 0 0] makefont       % Create a 20 degree obliqued 12
					    % point font.
  setfont
234 424 moveto
